compat-change.description: For accessibility services targeting APIs greater than {@link Build.VERSION_CODES#Q API 29}, {@link #FLAG_REQUEST_ACCESSIBILITY_BUTTON} must be specified in the accessibility service metadata file. Otherwise, it will be ignored.
compat-change.name: REQUEST_ACCESSIBILITY_BUTTON_CHANGE

compat-change.description: There will now be a callback to {@link android.content.SharedPreferences.OnSharedPreferenceChangeListener#onSharedPreferenceChanged OnSharedPreferenceChangeListener.onSharedPreferenceChanged} with a {@code null} key on {@link android.content.SharedPreferences.Editor#clear Editor.clear}.
compat-change.name: CALLBACK_ON_CLEAR_CHANGE

compat-change.description: Apps targeting Android R and above will need to declare the packages and intents they intend to use to get details about other apps on a device. Such declarations must be made via the {@code <queries>} tag in the manifest.
compat-change.name: FILTER_APPLICATION_QUERY

compat-change.description: Remove android.test.base library for apps that target SDK R or more and do not depend on android.test.runner (as it depends on classes from the android.test.base library).
compat-change.name: REMOVE_ANDROID_TEST_BASE

compat-change.description: Compat framework change ID for the APN db read permission change. In API level 30 and beyond, accessing the APN database will require the {@link android.Manifest.permission#WRITE_APN_SETTINGS} permission. This change ID tracks apps that are affected because they don't hold this permission.
compat-change.name: APN_READING_PERMISSION_CHANGE_ID

compat-change.description: To check the SDK version for {@code PreciseDataConnectionState#getDataConnectionState}.
compat-change.name: GET_DATA_CONNECTION_STATE_CODE_CHANGE

compat-change.description: To check the SDK version for SmsManager.sendResolverResult method.
compat-change.name: GET_TARGET_SDK_VERSION_CODE_CHANGE

compat-change.description: To expand the error codes for {@link TelephonyManager#updateAvailableNetworks} and {@link TelephonyManager#setPreferredOpportunisticDataSubscription}.
compat-change.name: CALLBACK_ON_MORE_ERROR_CODE_CHANGE

compat-change.description: To check the SDK version for {@link TelephonyManager#getDataState}.
compat-change.name: GET_DATA_STATE_CODE_CHANGE

compat-change.description: To check the SDK version for {@link TelephonyManager#listen}.
compat-change.name: LISTEN_CODE_CHANGE
